    title Papercut labs
  body
    
    .container
      .menu.row.mb-50
        .logo.col-md-4
          img(src="assets/img/papercut_logo.png", alt="", width="34px" class="img-fluid")
          span Papercutlabs
        .menu-title.col-md-8
          a(href="#") Home
          a(data-scroll href="#thingsdo") Things we do
          a(href="https://rittamdebnath.typeform.com/to/YuMAEP" target="_blank").btn Start a Project
    
    
      .page-title.row.mb-80
        .text-block.col-md-5
          p.block-title welcome to Papercut
          p.head-title
           | We Help Brands & Businesses Gain a Competitive Advantage in the Connected World.
        .img-block.col-md-7
          img(src="assets/img/head_computer.png", alt="" class="img-fluid")
          
          
      .things-we-do.row.mb-80#thingsdo
        .img-block.col-md-7
          img(src="assets/img/things_we_do_block.png", alt="" class="img-fluid")
        .text-block.col-md-5.ml-20
          .block-title.mb-40 things we do
          .text-block-group.mb-30
            .content-title web and mobile design
            .content
              p Design resides at the center of who we are. We believe that good design equals great business, realizing a simple and efficient experience for your visitors.
              
          .text-block-group.mb-30
            .content-title Branding and strategy
            .content
              p We make your stories come to life and maintain constant growth for your business while creating your unique brand that falls in place with your vision.
              
          .text-block-group
            .content-title development
            .content
              p Front-end development, CMS integration or optimal back-end support – you know we’ve got you covered. We make sure that your site is fast and smart.

      
      
      .value-added-1.row.mb-80
        .text-block.col-md-5
          .text-block-group.mb-60
            .content-title 
              img(src="assets/img/call.png") 
              span You can count on us

            .content
              p We value you. When you contact us, you can expect to hear back the same day. We work hard to make you look good.

          .text-block-group
            .content-title 
              img(src="assets/img/calendar.png", alt="")
              span We won't leave you hanging
            .content
              p We won’t just disappear after completing the project. We stick around with our long-term maintenance packages. Need to change something in the website at a moment’s notice? We got it covered
        .img-block.col-md-7
          img(src="assets/img/value_added_big_1.png", alt="" class="img-fluid")
        
        
      .value-added-2.row.mb-80
        .img-block.col-md-7
          img(src="assets/img/value_added_big_2.png", alt="" class="img-fluid")
        .text-block.col-md-5
          .text-block-group.mb-60
            .content-title 
              img(src="assets/img/speed.png", alt="")
              span We scale with you
            .content
              p Your development needs will change as your company and vision grows. Having a low? We scale down so you only pay for what you want to use.

          .text-block-group
            .content-title 
              img(src="assets/img/mac.png", alt="")
              span Top quality code
            .content
              p Nothing but top-notch, elegant and graceful code that actually does something. It is what fuels us and we wouldn’t have it any other way.

        
        
      .footer.row.mb-30
        .text-block.col-md-12.text-center.mb-50
          .block-title.mb-20 have a project in mind? let's chat
          hr
          .content.col-md-6
            p We’re ever looking to team up with new and booming companies with a vision to build something great. So if that’s you, hit us up!
          a(class="cta" href="https://rittamdebnath.typeform.com/to/YuMAEP" target="_blank") Start a Project
        .contact-block.row
          .img-block.col-md-6
            img(src="assets/img/girl.png", alt="")
          .company-info.col-md-4
            .content-title
              p contact
              a(href="mailto:papercutlabs@gmail.com?Subject=Start a project" target="_top") Papercutlabs@gmail.com
      .exit-block.row.mb-30
        .logo.col-md-4
          img(src="assets/img/papercut_logo.png", alt="", width="34px" class="img-fluid")
          span © 2017 Papercut
        .social-block.col-md-8
          a(href="https://www.facebook.com/PapercutLabs-371939749945680" target="_blank") Facebook
          a(href="https://twitter.com/papercutlab" target="_blank") Twitter
          a(href="http://instagram.com/papercut.labs" target="_blank") Instagram
          
    
    
